{"tid":2284501,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"限聚婚禮婚宴比人情？點比好呢","createTime":"2020-11-13T10:41:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T17:40:06.000Z","uid":188630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a418eb4800b595074617b03d7b5d0a2bd2296a45","tid":2284501,"uid":188630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T10:41:13.000Z","msg":"集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事緣朋友疫情期間訂左大埔海濱公園出年1月個場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到而家都無明確講係婚禮定婚宴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個場由12點去到6點<br />\n即使未有第4波，限聚都應不會變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n朋友都應好堅持搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知佢親戚朋友都好多<br />\n<br />\n但如果係無食物，即係婚禮，即係限50人啦，但律師證婚只係果十幾分鐘，照計佢親戚同兄弟姊妹都50人，即係被邀請嘅話，都可能係9 fing fing，等證婚完，果幾十人出嚟先入得去，又9 fing fing影幅相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果係有食物，又唔知點限聚法，戶外又計唔計6人一枱呢，但海濱疑似係無枱，立食到會野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇，點比人情好呢，其實定係勸佢簽個紙之後先補擺好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4975827f88b033981e4a0394455fa6f022e711","tid":2284501,"uid":81345,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a418eb4800b595074617b03d7b5d0a2bd2296a45","tid":2284501,"uid":188630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T10:41:13.000Z","msg":"集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事緣朋友疫情期間訂左大埔海濱公園出年1月個場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgm